Pre-req--  
sudo apt install openjdk-21-jdk -y  
sudo apt install unzip

then,  

cd /otp
sudo wget https://binaries.sonarsource.com/Distribution/sonar-scanner-cli/sonar-scanner-cli-8.1.0.6389.zip
unzip sonar-scanner-cli-8.1.0.6389.zip  
mv sonar-scanner-8.1.0.6389 sonar-scanner
sudo ln -s /opt/sonar-scanner/bin/sonar-scanner /usr/local/bin/sonar-scanner

after that,  
run --  sonar-scanner --version
if you see version detail and all then scanner is working.

